Package com.example.finalproject

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Earth_Fragment_Code.OnFragmentInteractionListener
    This interface must be implemented by activities that contain this fragment to allow an interaction in this fragment to be communicated to the activity and potentially other fragments contained in that activity.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Earth_Favorites
    Launches the list of favorites activity Launches a screen that displays a list of all the images that have been saved to the database
    Earth_Fragment_Code
    This fragment contains the info about a certain image from the list A simple Fragment subclass.
    Earth_Fragment_Frame
    This class creates the fragment and places it into the frame of the empty layout
    Earth_Image
    Launches the Image display activity This launches a screen with the results of the search, including the image date, coordinates and the image itself
    Earth_Main
    Launches the main menu of the Earth image search activity launches a screen with 3 buttons, a toolbar and a navigation menu, different screens will be launches depending on which buttons are clicked
    Earth_Search
    Launches the search activity of the nasa image search Displays a screen displaying the search fields for the image and a search button and a button to display the last search done
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    MainActivity
    Launcher activity for the Final Project application AppCompatActivity subclass.
